# Estrutura de Dados

# Match

```ts
type Match = {
  homeTeam: string;
  awayTeam: string;

  kickoff: string;

  method: "LAY_00" | "LAY_FAVORITE";

  stats: MatchStats;
}
```

---

# TeamStats

```ts
type TeamStats = {
  goalsAvg65: number;

  concededAvg65: number;

  htGoalRate: number;

  over15Rate: number;

  scoredTimeline: number[];

  concededTimeline: number[];
}
```

---

# Algoritmo dos Métodos

# Lay 0x0

```txt
Se:

goalsAvg65 >= 0.85

E

htGoalRate >= 80%

E

over15Rate >= 85%

→ jogo elegível
```

---

# Lay Favorito

```txt
Favorito:
goalsAvg70 >= 0.85

Adversário:
concededAvg65 >= 0.85
```

